strings: <voice_0x01000CDB><se_low>King of tricks: ... read on Angela, it seems like everyone is rooting for you!
<voice_0x01000CDD><se_low>King of tricks: Will it help to get rid of the breasts? Note that I don't want to force...
<voice_0x01000CDE><se_def>China: ... I know. we might never recover. Marcellus will never forgive me.
<voice_0x01000CDF><se_def>China: If we weren't related we would be together.

<voice_0x01000CE0><se_def><center>Abbe Francisco has always been known
<center>for his kindness in these places.
<center>Take in a child who has nowhere else to go.

<voice_0x01000CE1><se_def><center>I'm one of them...
<center>My parents are rich and wealthy.
<center>But then everyone dies...

<voice_0x01000CE2><se_def><center>And suddenly I lost my family
<center>and money. The only place
<center>he can go is a monastery.
<voice_0x01000CE3><se_def>Awesome!: ...is this your first time here?
<voice_0x01000CE4><se_def>Awesome!: You and your brother came alone.
<voice_0x01000CE5><se_def>Awesome!: Ha... you must be tired. where are your belongings?
<voice_0x01000CE6><se_high>China: After all, my parents aren't alive anymore. I have nothing, so I won't go anywhere...
<voice_0x01000CE7><se_def>Awesome!: ...reminds me of many things. But don't worry, from now on Abbot Francesco and we are all his family.
<voice_0x01000CE8><se_high>China: fine...
<voice_0x01000CE9><se_def>Awesome!: ... Let's go to the abbot, don't cry, because you won't tell me your name
<voice_0x01000CEA><se_high>China: ... Welcome
<voice_0x01000CEB><se_def>Awesome!: you are an angel
<voice_0x01000CEC><se_def>Awesome!: ... very well.
<voice_0x01000CED><se_def>Awesome!: I want you to go and never come back. I do not want to see you anymore!
<voice_0x01000CEE>Awesome!: ............
<voice_0x01000CEF><se_def>Awesome!: So you want to ruin my life too?

<voice_0x01000CF0><se_def><center>He was Marcello Mata's golden boy
<center>who is academically brilliant
<center>and has a bright future ahead.

<voice_0x01000CF1><se_def><center>But when he talks about me
<center>his attitude is not positive.
<voice_0x01000CF2><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: ... forgive me, little girl. Sorry for the short conversation.
<voice_0x01000CF3><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: This behavior is very different from Marcelo's, I don't understand...
<voice_0x01000CF4><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: to look...
<voice_0x01000CF5><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: You always knew I had a half-brother... right?
<voice_0x01000CF6><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: All wounds will heal with time...Hope we are all doing well here, he added.
<voice_0x01000CF7><se_low>San Francisco Monastery: This will be your home from now on. Want to recommend them all?

<voice_0x01000CF8><se_def><center>... after a while
<center>I heard the whole story
<center>for the first time.

<voice_0x01000CF9><se_def><center>He has a half-brother because his father
<center>had an affair with a farmer's daughter
<center>before they were married.

<voice_0x01000CFA><se_def><center>He banished his wife and children,
<center>who were considered his mother's lovers.

<voice_0x01000CFB><se_def><center>It seems that the poor were penniless.
<center>He said that he could not bear the terrible pain and could not live.
<center>And she was left in the world alone.
<center>This is Marcelo's story, okay?
<voice_0x01000CFD><se_def><center>When a mother says she has no children.

<voice_0x01000CFE><se_def><center>The doctor must have been wrong,
<center>however, because the mother
<center>soon became pregnant.

<voice_0x01000CFF><se_def><center>This prevents the idea
<center>of adoption and suddenly
<center>sends Marcelo to a monastery.

<voice_0x01000D00><se_def><center>Marcelo has been abandoned
<center>by his biological father twice...
<center>Marcelo hates his father
<center>and of course I hate him too."
<voice_0x01000D01><se_def>China: Don't you think it's a bomb? I was young and innocent then. It's all more painful than you can imagine.
<voice_0x01000D02><se_def>China: But life has to go on.
<voice_0x01000D03><se_def>China: He was right, he did what he wanted, then he died and I got my revenge.
<voice_0x01000D04><se_def>China: Marcello, you hate me now.
<voice_0x01000D05><se_def>China: ... I am not trying to criticize. And it will be fun with you. At least this guy will hold you accountable.
<voice_0x01000D06><se_def>China: This will surely brighten up my boring life Matt.
<voice_0x01000D07><se_low>King of tricks: Angel...
<voice_0x01000D08><se_def>China: enough! It's almost dawn!
<voice_0x01000D09><se_low>King of tricks: I wait!
